# Keeping tmp/ gitignored is just good hygiene. The skills here write their scratch and
# result files under tmp/, and scsh's own `run` preflight requires tmp/ to be gitignored.
# This file is authoring infra, not shipped to consumers (scsh installskills sets that up
# there); it lives here purely for in-repo sanity and to spare models false positives over
# untracked scratch files.
tmp/
